derivation: or (feminine) שִׁבֹּלֶת; from the same as H7640 (שֹׁבֶל);
outline:
1. flowing stream
  2. ear (of grain), head of grain
    1. as growing
    2. cluster
kjv_def: branch, channel, ear (of corn), (water-)flood, Shibboleth. Compare H5451 (סִבֹּלֶת).
strongs_def: a stream (as flowing); also an ear of grain (as growing out); by analogy, a branch
